{"type":"message","id":"18b4ebcf","parentId":"2a610f1e","timestamp":"2026-02-26T12:01:42.833Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2f05f2f4460d46d4becf680d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"image-recognition\n\n  /**\n   * 通用图片识别工具，识别图片中的文字内容和信息\n   *\n   * @param image_url? 要识别的图片URL地址\n   * @param image_data? 图片的base64编码数据（以data:开头）\n   * @param custom_prompt? 自定义识别提示词（可选）\n   * @param min_pixels? 输入图像的最小像素阈值\n   * @param max_pixels? 输入图像的最大像素阈值\n   */\n  function recognize_image(image_url?: string, image_data?: string, custom_prompt?: string, min_pixels?: number, max_pixels?: number);\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call image-recognition.recognize_image(min_pixels: 3136, max_pixe, ...)\n\n  1 tool · 3062ms · STDIO npx -y @mcpcn/image-recognition-mcp"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3954,"aggregated":"image-recognition\n\n  /**\n   * 通用图片识别工具，识别图片中的文字内容和信息\n   *\n   * @param image_url? 要识别的图片URL地址\n   * @param image_data? 图片的base64编码数据（以data:开头）\n   * @param custom_prompt? 自定义识别提示词（可选）\n   * @param min_pixels? 输入图像的最小像素阈值\n   * @param max_pixels? 输入图像的最大像素阈值\n   */\n  function recognize_image(image_url?: string, image_data?: string, custom_prompt?: string, min_pixels?: number, max_pixels?: number);\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call image-recognition.recognize_image(min_pixels: 3136, max_pixe, ...)\n\n  1 tool · 3062ms · STDIO npx -y @mcpcn/image-recognition-mcp","cwd":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772107302829}}
{"type":"message","id":"19e1e92f","parentId":"18b4ebcf","timestamp":"2026-02-26T12:01:50.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"image-recognition 只支持 image_url 和 image_data，不支持本地路径。\n\n让我换个思路：把图片文件复制到工作区，然后用一个简单的方式生成 URL 或者用 base64。\n\n或者，让我试试用 web 服务的方式。但这样太复杂了。\n\n最简单的方式：让我用 Python 脚本把 base64 数据写入文件，然后用 mcporter 从 stdin 读取？不行，mcporter 不支持这种方式。\n\n让我试试用 PowerShell 把 base64 数据分段传递，或者用临时 HTTP 服务器。\n\n其实，最简单的方法是：让我用 Python 的 http.server 临时启动一个 HTTP 服务器，然后用 image_url 参数访问。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_22f197f2ea8d489296215479","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import http.server\nimport socketserver\nimport threading\nimport time\nimport subprocess\nimport os\n\n# 切换到目标目录\nos.chdir(r'D:\\虚拟人\\人设集合\\大厂搬砖工')\n\n# 获取第一个 jpg 文件\nfiles = [f for f in os.listdir('.') if f.endswith('.jpg')]\ntarget_file = files[0]\nprint(f'Target file: {target_file}')\n\n# 启动简单的 HTTP 服务器\nPORT = 8765\nhandler = http.server.SimpleHTTPRequestHandler\n\nhttpd = socketserver.TCPServer((\"\", PORT), handler)\nserver_thread = threading.Thread(target=httpd.serve_forever)\nserver_thread.daemon = True\nserver_thread.start()\n\nprint(f'HTTP server started on port {PORT}')\ntime.sleep(1)\n\n# 调用 mcporter\nimage_url = f'http://localhost:{PORT}/{target_file}'\ncmd = f'mcporter call image-recognition.recognize_image image_url=\"{image_url}\"'\nprint(f'Running: {cmd}')\nresult = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, shell=True)\n\nprint(\"=== RESULT ===\")\nprint(result.stdout)\nif result.stderr:\n    print(\"STDERR:\", result.stderr)\n\nhttpd.shutdown()\nprint('Done')\n","file_path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\ocr_http.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":165207,"output":620,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":165827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772107302834}